import colorlessFrameImage from "./colorless_frame.png" 
import whiteFrameImage from "./white_frame.png" 
import blueFrameImage from "./blue_frame.png" 
import blackFrameImage from "./black_frame.png" 
import redFrameImage from "./red_frame.png" 
import greenFrameImage from "./green_frame.png" 
import goldenFrameImage from "./golden_frame.png" 
import greyFrameImage from "./grey_frame.png" 
import hybridWhiteBlueFrameImage from "./hybrid_white_blue_frame.png" 
import hybridWhiteBlackFrameImage from "./hybrid_white_black_frame.png" 
import hybridRedWhiteFrameImage from "./hybrid_red_white_frame.png" 
import hybridRedGreenFrameImage from "./hybrid_red_green_frame.png" 
import hybridGreenBlueFrameImage from "./hybrid_green_blue_frame.png" 
import hybridGreenWhiteFrameImage from "./hybrid_green_white_frame.png" 
import hybridBlueBlackFrameImage from "./hybrid_blue_black_frame.png" 
import hybridBlueRedFrameImage from "./hybrid_blue_red_frame.png" 
import hybridBlackRedFrameImage from "./hybrid_black_red_frame.png" 
import hybridBlackGreenFrameImage from "./hybrid_black_green_frame.png" 
import colorlessPTFrameImage from "./colorless_creature_frame.png" 
import whitePTFrameImage from "./white_creature_frame.png" 
import bluePTFrameImage from "./blue_creature_frame.png" 
import blackPTFrameImage from "./black_creature_frame.png" 
import redPTFrameImage from "./red_creature_frame.png" 
import greenPTFrameImage from "./green_creature_frame.png" 
import goldenPTFrameImage from "./golden_creature_frame.png" 
import greyPTFrameImage from "./grey_creature_frame.png" 
import hybridWhiteBluePTFrameImage from "./hybrid_white_blue_creature_frame.png" 
import hybridWhiteBlackPTFrameImage from "./hybrid_white_black_creature_frame.png" 
import hybridRedWhitePTFrameImage from "./hybrid_red_white_creature_frame.png" 
import hybridRedGreenPTFrameImage from "./hybrid_red_green_creature_frame.png" 
import hybridGreenBluePTFrameImage from "./hybrid_green_blue_creature_frame.png" 
import hybridGreenWhitePTFrameImage from "./hybrid_green_white_creature_frame.png" 
import hybridBlueBlackPTFrameImage from "./hybrid_blue_black_creature_frame.png" 
import hybridBlueRedPTFrameImage from "./hybrid_blue_red_creature_frame.png" 
import hybridBlackRedPTFrameImage from "./hybrid_black_red_creature_frame.png" 
import hybridBlackGreenPTFrameImage from "./hybrid_black_green_creature_frame.png" 

export const frames = { "Colorless": [colorlessFrameImage, colorlessPTFrameImage],
                        "White": [whiteFrameImage, whitePTFrameImage],
                        "Blue": [blueFrameImage, bluePTFrameImage],
                        "Black": [blackFrameImage, blackPTFrameImage],
                        "Red": [redFrameImage, redPTFrameImage],
                        "Green": [greenFrameImage, greenPTFrameImage],
                        "Golden": [goldenFrameImage, goldenPTFrameImage],
                        "Grey": [greyFrameImage, greyPTFrameImage],
                        "Hybrid White/Blue": [hybridWhiteBlueFrameImage, hybridWhiteBluePTFrameImage],
                        "Hybrid White/Black": [hybridWhiteBlackFrameImage, hybridWhiteBlackPTFrameImage],
                        "Hybrid Red/White": [hybridRedWhiteFrameImage, hybridRedWhitePTFrameImage],
                        "Hybrid Red/Green": [hybridRedGreenFrameImage, hybridRedGreenPTFrameImage],
                        "Hybrid Green/Blue": [hybridGreenBlueFrameImage, hybridGreenBluePTFrameImage],
                        "Hybrid Green/White": [hybridGreenWhiteFrameImage, hybridGreenWhitePTFrameImage],    
                        "Hybrid Blue/Black": [hybridBlueBlackFrameImage, hybridBlueBlackPTFrameImage],
                        "Hybrid Blue/Red": [hybridBlueRedFrameImage, hybridBlueRedPTFrameImage],
                        "Hybrid Black/Red": [hybridBlackRedFrameImage, hybridBlackRedPTFrameImage],
                        "Hybrid Black/Green": [hybridBlackGreenFrameImage, hybridBlackGreenPTFrameImage] }
